title: Bug 121170: get column label from meta data object should return some user recognizable strings
OB: The behavior of IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before/after data extraction is different.
EB: Calling IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before/after data extraction should return the same labels.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Call IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before data extraction.
2. Call IMetaData.getColumnLabel() after data extraction.
3. Compare the results and observe the difference.
